00:02:43,997 --> 00:02:47,132
bottom of the utilities window there, inside other views.

62
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:48,132
So you can drag,

63
00:02:48,201 --> 00:02:51,703
do it by dragging-dropping inside of other views.

