00:06:31,624 --> 00:06:33,425
do it in Interface Builder with Xcode.

147
00:06:33,494 --> 00:06:37,261
But, so that's the kind of in-code one.

148
00:06:37,330 --> 00:06:40,097
And init with this coder thing,

